.TH backup 1  "backup " 
.SH NAME
backup \- Create a content\-addressed snapshot
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBbackup\fR [\fB\-\-description\fR] [\fB\-\-threads\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] [\fIPATH\fR] 
.SH DESCRIPTION
Create a content\-addressed snapshot
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-description\fR \fI<DESCRIPTION>\fR

.TP
\fB\-\-threads\fR \fI<THREADS>\fR [default: 0]
Scanner threads (1 disables parallelism, 0 uses all available CPUs)
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.TP
[\fIPATH\fR] [default: .]

